Table 8  Incident dialysis patients with late referral status,* by province/territory and Canada, 2012 to 2021 (percentage)
* Patients with a late referral status started dialysis less than 90 days after first seeing a nephrologist.

Data from Quebec was excluded for 2012 to 2019 due to significant under-reporting of dialysis data between 2011 and 2019. While dialysis data submission for Quebec recommenced in 2020, there still exists potential for under-reporting of incidence in 2020–2021.
Canadian Organ Replacement Register, 2022, Canadian Institute for Health Information.
